<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="55600000t" end="64600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">大号的那只呢？</p>
<p begin="68300000t" end="97300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">啊  正被羽川姐姐照看着</p>
<p begin="120100000t" end="145100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">那就给我讲讲细节吧</p>
<p begin="146600000t" end="193800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">嗯  讲倒是可以  不过在这之前能不能答应我一件事？</p>
<p begin="194600000t" end="211400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">你有什么立场可以跟我讲条件</p>
<p begin="212700000t" end="235100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">我是站在妹妹的立场所以可以讲</p>
<p begin="236700000t" end="254400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">我是站在哥哥的立场所以我拒绝</p>
<p begin="287600000t" end="307100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">明白了  那我放弃</p>
<p begin="310300000t" end="337400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">话说你打算提出什么条件？</p>
<p begin="338700000t" end="362400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">我想让你答应「不要生火怜的气」</p>
<p begin="363700000t" end="370400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">不行</p>
<p begin="371700000t" end="410900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">那就「可以生我的气  但是不要生火怜的气」</p>
<p begin="412000000t" end="422100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">你们哪个都跑不了</p>
<p begin="423400000t" end="458600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">那就「可以生火怜的气  但是不要生我的气」</p>
<p begin="459900000t" end="473900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">话说我已经生气了</p>
<p begin="475700000t" end="490600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">赶紧给我老实交代  然后就没你的事了</p>
<p begin="502300000t" end="555100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">说得倒是好听  明明在羽川姐姐面前都答应不生气了</p>
<p begin="560600000t" end="597900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">哥哥你就没有做过什么觉得后悔的事情么？</p>
<p begin="599800000t" end="625600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">后悔？我一直都在后悔啊</p>
<p begin="628000000t" end="645000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">哪有人会不后悔的</p>
<p begin="646200000t" end="691800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">该怎么说呢  我就是那种不怎么后悔的人</p>
<p begin="698500000t" end="725400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">也是  你们两姐妹就是那种性格</p>
<p begin="728000000t" end="748200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">不过…正因如此…</p>
<p begin="753200000t" end="809500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">有时也会因为「当时为什么不后悔呢」而后悔</p>
<p begin="868400000t" end="882000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">算了  反正也无所谓</p>
<p begin="893000000t" end="918400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">我看你的脖子是找掐了吧</p>
<p begin="919900000t" end="939900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">不…不是这么回事</p>
<p begin="946200000t" end="965400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">那就赶紧回到正题</p>
<p begin="967400000t" end="999900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">啊  对了哥哥  给你讲件好事</p>
<p begin="1001400000t" end="1010200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">好事？</p>
<p begin="1011600000t" end="1046900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">关于我的口头禅「白金火大」</p>
<p begin="1011600000t" end="1046900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">プラチナむかつく</p>
<p begin="1049300000t" end="1079300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">那个本来是从「微火大」演变过来的</p>
<p begin="1049300000t" end="1079300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">プチむかつく</p>
<p begin="1081200000t" end="1125800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">而不是形容火大到让人能联想到白金的程度</p>
<p begin="1127700000t" end="1160000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">你有「白金火大」这个口头禅我都是第一次听说</p>
<p begin="1161600000t" end="1187500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">你怎么能不知道  真让人白金火大！</p>
<p begin="1189000000t" end="1207000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">你这明明就是很火大嘛！</p>
<p begin="1209100000t" end="1239500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">话说  不许你再这么巧妙地转变话题了</p>
<p begin="1242400000t" end="1254900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">那么…哥哥</p>
<p begin="1257300000t" end="1300390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">先跟我说说什么让你感到后悔的事情吧</p>
<p begin="1303200000t" end="1329000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">我想听听哥哥的后悔故事</p>
<p begin="1330700000t" end="1337300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">啥？</p>
<p begin="1339400000t" end="1363300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">让我一个人交代总有点不甘心</p>
<p begin="1365400000t" end="1398900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">能不能换成互相吐露秘密的形式</p>
<p begin="1400700000t" end="1418200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">就像修学旅行的卧谈会那样</p>
<p begin="1423900000t" end="1434700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">你傻啊</p>
<p begin="1435900000t" end="1467100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">不过  说起我的后悔故事…</p>
<p begin="1469000000t" end="1493800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">你这么直截了当地问我  我还真不知道该怎么说</p>
<p begin="1497900000t" end="1527100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">就是感觉有点丢脸的事情就行</p>
<p begin="1529400000t" end="1548000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">比如说…</p>
<p begin="1551700000t" end="1581800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">哥哥为什么交不到朋友</p>
<p begin="1582900000t" end="1590800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">我现在有朋友！</p>
<p begin="1591900000t" end="1605800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">是吗  几个？</p>
<p begin="1607500000t" end="1618200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">你要问几个？</p>
<p begin="1620500000t" end="1633300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">说出来吓你一跳！</p>
<p begin="1657100000t" end="1664600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">五个！</p>
<p begin="1686600000t" end="1698500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">还真是吓了我一跳</p>
<p begin="1701400000t" end="1740200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">哥哥好可怜  这辈子肯定会一个人寂寞而死啊</p>
<p begin="1741500000t" end="1758700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">还真敢跟你亲哥哥说这么过分的话啊</p>
<p begin="1763900000t" end="1814300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">先不提现在  说起曾经的某个时期我为什么没有朋友…</p>
<p begin="1818800000t" end="1851700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">没错  我曾经是这么想的…</p>
<p begin="1855900000t" end="1873700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">一旦和别人交起朋友  人类的强度就会…</p>
<p begin="1874900000t" end="1909500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">不用了  你之前讲的就已经很丢脸了  你不用说了</p>
<p begin="1914400000t" end="1932200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">对不起问了你这么奇怪的问题</p>
<p begin="1933000000t" end="1968300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">先别对我道歉  我还没说过什么丢人的事呢</p>
<p begin="1969100000t" end="1987300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">别这样  哥哥  你不用说了</p>
<p begin="1988700000t" end="2012300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">不要再往自己的伤口上撒盐了</p>
<p begin="2014500000t" end="2036400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">别这样  就到此为止吧</p>
<p begin="2037500000t" end="2047600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">为止你个头啊！</p>
<p begin="2049300000t" end="2082400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">阿良良木君  我在二楼都听见你的声音了</p>
<p begin="2084500000t" end="2119600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">我知道你们是在闲聊</p>
<p begin="2121900000t" end="2144500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">不过就不能稍微小点声说吗？</p>
<p begin="2154100000t" end="2167900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">啊  不好意思</p>
<p begin="2174200000t" end="2180100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">我会注意…</p>
<p begin="2254200000t" end="2290500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">火怜与蜜蜂  其五</p>
<p begin="2454300000t" end="2492300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">今朝目が覚めたら  忘れちゃった</p>
<p begin="2454300000t" end="2492300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">今早睁开眼睛  差点忘了</p>
<p begin="2503100000t" end="2564400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">夢の続き  まだあたし待っていた</p>
<p begin="2503100000t" end="2564400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">昨天的梦  依然在等我去延续</p>
<p begin="2565500000t" end="2602600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">運命だよこれ  ほっとけない</p>
<p begin="2565500000t" end="2602600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">这就是命运  不能置之不理</p>
<p begin="2611600000t" end="2668800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">理由があるんだ  正義の味方だから</p>
<p begin="2611600000t" end="2668800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">我可是有理由的  因为我是正义的伙伴</p>
<p begin="2675300000t" end="2781400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">燃えるこの温度に  溶けるその答えは</p>
<p begin="2675300000t" end="2781400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">融化于炙热的温度中  这份答案就是</p>
<p begin="2784100000t" end="2854300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">清く正しくそして格好良く</p>
<p begin="2784100000t" end="2854300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">光明磊落  正直善良  帅气无比</p>
<p begin="2856000000t" end="2884700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">なくちゃね</p>
<p begin="2856000000t" end="2884700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">就这么简单</p>
<p begin="2886100000t" end="2938800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">手をつなぎ  どこまでも行こう</p>
<p begin="2886100000t" end="2938800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">牵起双手  勇往直前吧</p>
<p begin="2941100000t" end="2993700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">頭より先に早く</p>
<p begin="2941100000t" end="2993700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">别想那么多</p>
<p begin="2995000000t" end="3046800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">君となら  どこまでも行ける</p>
<p begin="2995000000t" end="3046800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">和你一起  世界任我行</p>
<p begin="3049700000t" end="3106000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">きっと  ずっと  もっと</p>
<p begin="3049700000t" end="3106000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">一定能  始终  更进一步</p>
<p begin="3089000000t" end="3189000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">本字幕仅供交流试看之用，如您喜欢本作品，请支持购买正版。</p>
<p begin="3089000000t" end="3189000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">翻译、校对：痛爱的飞鱼、维京风暴、detectivexsc；</p>
<p begin="3218000000t" end="3242900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">先说说阿良良木火怜那边的事</p>
<p begin="3247800000t" end="3277800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">话虽如此  也不过是我听过羽川和月火的描述</p>
<p begin="3280100000t" end="3330800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">将内容综合后的回想画面  可能和实际有出入</p>
<p begin="3342000000t" end="3372500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">欢迎欢迎  小姑娘  我就是贝木</p>
<p begin="3376100000t" end="3398400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">贝塚的贝  枯木的木</p>
<p begin="3404100000t" end="3424400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">你的名字呢</p>
<p begin="3426100000t" end="3440400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">阿良良木火怜</p>
<p begin="3442900000t" end="3459100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">左耳旁加可能性的可</p>
<p begin="3461700000t" end="3486400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">良好的良两个  再加上若木的木</p>
<p begin="3488700000t" end="3510400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">最后是火和怜悯的怜  火怜</p>
<p begin="3513300000t" end="3546000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">名字不错  回家别忘感谢你爸妈</p>
<p begin="3594300000t" end="3613900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">那么你是为什么目的而来的</p>
<p begin="3616300000t" end="3669500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">想让我教你咒语？还是帮你解除咒语？</p>
<p begin="3671800000t" end="3700300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">前者一万  后者两万</p>
<p begin="3702200000t" end="3716700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">哪个都不是</p>
<p begin="3718200000t" end="3732500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">我是来扁你的</p>
<p begin="3733900000t" end="3802400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">来扁我？呵  也就是说用假邮件把我骗出来自投罗网吗</p>
<p begin="3804600000t" end="3833100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">原来如此  手段是不错</p>
<p begin="3840500000t" end="3874300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">话说回来  这又不像是你的手段呢</p>
<p begin="3884000000t" end="3943600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">像你这种头脑简单的家伙根本不可能找到我</p>
<p begin="3964400000t" end="3984900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">应该没有人指使你吧</p>
<p begin="3988500000t" end="4040200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">像现在这样能站到我面前真是有点超出寻常了</p>
<p begin="4066400000t" end="4117800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">你做的事让大家很困扰  这就不需要我一一提醒了吧</p>
<p begin="4119300000t" end="4135600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">哪有什么困扰</p>
<p begin="4137700000t" end="4173600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">我只是把你们想要的东西卖给你们而已</p>
<p begin="4177000000t" end="4196900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">剩下的本就该你们自己负责吧</p>
<p begin="4198200000t" end="4211200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">自己负责…</p>
<p begin="4221800000t" end="4243500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">什么自己负责啊  你开玩笑吧</p>
<p begin="4246300000t" end="4290200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">把大家的人际关系搞得一团糟  你到底有什么目的</p>
<p begin="4292900000t" end="4328900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">有什么目的吗  这问题可真深刻</p>
<p begin="4334800000t" end="4388900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">可遗憾的是对于如此深刻的问题  我的回答却很肤浅</p>
<p begin="4396200000t" end="4417800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">只有一个字  那就是钱</p>
<p begin="4419700000t" end="4434800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">钱？</p>
<p begin="4437700000t" end="4466600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">这世上钱就是一切</p>
<p begin="4472000000t" end="4525800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">你似乎是抱着某种无聊的正义感而来的  真的很可惜</p>
<p begin="4527900000t" end="4559100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">这种行为  至少能向委托人要上十万</p>
<p begin="4562200000t" end="4623100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">这次事件中你应该得到的教训是  干白工很不划算</p>
<p begin="4630400000t" end="4682100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">要你个头的委托人啊  没人拜托我这样做</p>
<p begin="4684800000t" end="4719200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">是吗  我还以为是谁要你这么做的呢</p>
<p begin="4720300000t" end="4744000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">就算有人要我这么做  我也不会要钱</p>
<p begin="4746100000t" end="4784600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">这就是年轻啊  但我不会羡慕你</p>
<p begin="4799300000t" end="4830100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">怎么了  你在发抖哦  阿良良木</p>
<p begin="4833700000t" end="4851100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">鬼才在发抖呢</p>
<p begin="4878400000t" end="4910900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">阿良良木  你刚才问过我的目的了吧</p>
<p begin="4913200000t" end="4953700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">现在该轮到我问你了  你的目的又是什么</p>
<p begin="4958300000t" end="4991900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">我早就说过了  我是来扁你的</p>
<p begin="5003400000t" end="5015100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">只是扁我吗</p>
<p begin="5022100000t" end="5036000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">我还要踹你呢</p>
<p begin="5039800000t" end="5050100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">要用暴力吗</p>
<p begin="5051300000t" end="5059800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">这叫武力</p>
<p begin="5061400000t" end="5087200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">然后我要阻止你继续做那些事</p>
<p begin="5088900000t" end="5125200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">对初中生做这种贪得无厌的交易  你到底在想什么</p>
<p begin="5128500000t" end="5140590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">你还算个大人吗</p>
<p begin="5144800000t" end="5160800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">这就是大人</p>
<p begin="5167990000t" end="5199500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">而且那些贪得无厌的交易也是理所当然</p>
<p begin="5225490000t" end="5245400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">因为我可是个欺诈师</p>
<p begin="5268000000t" end="5295700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">对初中生下手  你就不觉得害臊吗</p>
<p begin="5296600000t" end="5344000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">一点也不  正因为是小孩子所以好骗  仅此而已</p>
<p begin="5348300000t" end="5419100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">但是阿良良木哟  想让我收手的话先别着急动武</p>
<p begin="5420800000t" end="5447600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">还是用钱收买我来的比较快</p>
<p begin="5451500000t" end="5485300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">这次我的营业目标是三百万</p>
<p begin="5491200000t" end="5517700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">从开始布局到现在已经花了两个多月时间</p>
<p begin="5520600000t" end="5552500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">不赚到那么多我连成本都赚不回来</p>
<p begin="5553800000t" end="5578100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">你…你还算是人吗</p>
<p begin="5582800000t" end="5607800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">很不巧  这就是人</p>
<p begin="5612200000t" end="5658500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">为保住重要的东西宁愿赌上性命的一般人而已</p>
<p begin="5660800000t" end="5686000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">你是日行一善来实现精神上的满足</p>
<p begin="5688900000t" end="5722300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">我则是日行一恶来实现钱包里的满足</p>
<p begin="5723700000t" end="5743700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">你说这又有什么区别呢</p>
<p begin="5745500000t" end="5760700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">区  区别…</p>
<p begin="5763200000t" end="5781000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">没错  根本没有区别</p>
<p begin="5784100000t" end="5823300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">也许你要用你的行为让某些人幸福</p>
<p begin="5827000000t" end="5897600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">但这和我用赚来的钱去刺激资本主义经济毫无二致</p>
<p begin="5905300000t" end="5931700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">这次事件中你该得到的教训是</p>
<p begin="5934400000t" end="5989500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">正义确实是无所不能的  但金钱也同样无所不能</p>
<p begin="6027100000t" end="6079400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">因我而「被害」的家伙也是一样  他们都付钱给我了</p>
<p begin="6083000000t" end="6119300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">这就是说他们用钱来认可了交易背后的代价</p>
<p begin="6124000000t" end="6142700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">你不也是一样吗  阿良良木</p>
<p begin="6147800000t" end="6188200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">难道说你身上那件运动衫买时没有付钱吗</p>
<p begin="6189400000t" end="6214100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">不  不许你提我的运动衫</p>
<p begin="6225200000t" end="6242800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">够了  快点下结论吧</p>
<p begin="6245100000t" end="6269000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">你是想吃我的拳头  还是…</p>
<p begin="6272300000t" end="6304800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">拳头我不想吃  脚也不想</p>
<p begin="6310500000t" end="6322700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">我不喜欢疼痛</p>
<p begin="6328500000t" end="6365200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">所以  我打算送你只蜜蜂做礼物</p>
<p begin="6681600000t" end="6730200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">效果很明显嘛  看来你还真是说什么就信什么的类型</p>
<p begin="6734500000t" end="6759400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">这次事件中你该得到的教训是</p>
<p begin="6762300000t" end="6788400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">要随时把陌生人当做欺诈师提防</p>
<p begin="6793700000t" end="6826600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">记得以后要见人三分疑</p>
<p begin="6829500000t" end="6876500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">但如果妄想叫我向你低头认罪  那你就太愚蠢了</p>
<p begin="6879200000t" end="6902500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">想让我洗手不干就去攒钱吧</p>
<p begin="6905200000t" end="6925000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">最少得有一千万  我才会考虑考虑</p>
<p begin="6934200000t" end="6947100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">你做了什么…</p>
<p begin="6951000000t" end="6973200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">你对我…做了什么…</p>
<p begin="6975800000t" end="7024600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">做了坏事呗  而且当然要收费的  钱我就不客气了</p>
