<p begin="7100700000t" end="7132000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">剩下点零钱给你坐车吧</p>
<p begin="7137500000t" end="7158600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">怎么  你有月票啊</p>
<p begin="7162900000t" end="7183500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">那零钱也不需要了吧</p>
<p begin="7190800000t" end="7223100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">再过一会儿毒就会安定下来  身体就能动了</p>
