<p begin="7263300000t" end="7288000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">我就趁机跑路好了</p>
<p begin="7292100000t" end="7316800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">我的生意当然还是会继续的</p>
<p begin="7323200000t" end="7375000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">不过  直接和客户见面这种事今后要尽量避免</p>
