<p begin="10317100000t" end="10345990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">洗好澡后就半裸跳舞的家伙  还真有脸说</p>
<p begin="10352600000t" end="10380600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">不是跳舞  那是有氧运动</p>
<p begin="10439400000t" end="10461190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">我帮你擦背  转过身去</p>
<p begin="10482700000t" end="10504300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">烦死了  帮我转</p>
<p begin="10528700000t" end="10540200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">可恶…</p>
<p begin="10555000000t" end="10577800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">真是大意了啊</p>
<p begin="10578800000t" end="10586400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">啊？</p>
<p begin="10600700000t" end="10654500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">就算哥哥不说  我也知道比起正确  强大更加重要</p>
<p begin="10657900000t" end="10684300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">但是  人又不能一下子变强</p>
<p begin="10688800000t" end="10735400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">所以在没有变强的时候  就要无视眼前所发生的不正当行为</p>
<p begin="10737800000t" end="10755800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">我怎么可能做得到</p>
<p begin="10759800000t" end="10797000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">我身体里所流淌的正义之血不会放过任何邪恶</p>
<p begin="10799600000t" end="10829800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">在我看来你只是想尽情胡闹吧</p>
<p begin="10832100000t" end="10867600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">当然在哥哥来看可能只是儿戏而已</p>
<p begin="10870300000t" end="10887800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">但是  贝木…</p>
